headline: Leidos and VML debut Imperium™, new AI-powered platform to enhance U.S. strategic information operations
summary: Leidos (NYSE:LDOS) a national security leader, and VML (NYSE: WPP), a global communications company, have created Imperium, a new artificial intelligence (AI)-powered technology platform designed to enhance U.S. capabilities to conduct information operations.

headline: What to Expect From Leidos Holdings’ Next Quarterly Earnings Report
summary: Leidos Holdings will release its third-quarter earnings next month, and analysts anticipate its EPS to fall in lower-double-digits.
